metadata.name: Divine Comedy
metadata.description:
"Most of humanity still hasn't realised that we're in the middle of a script" - Zinastar Mahadevi

If you're happy in your life then you're responsible for that. But if you're miserable? Guess who's also responsible?

Everything unfolding right now is doing so with Divine grace. Heaven is a place on earth but so is hell. It's always up to us which reality we wish to live in. Choose consciously.
